Installation Instructions
=========================

Prerequisites:

    - C17 compiler (gcc, clang, etc.)
    - ncurses development headers (libncursesw)
    - SQLite 3 is bundled in lib/

Quick install:

    ./configure
    make
    make check
    sudo make install

This installs browse-sqlite3 (and a bs3 symlink) to $prefix/bin and
the manpage to $prefix/share/man/man1.

To specify an install prefix:

    ./configure --prefix=/usr/local

To uninstall:

    sudo make uninstall

Standard targets:

    make            Build the binary
    make install    Install program, alias, and manpage
    make uninstall  Remove installed files
    make clean      Remove all build artifacts
    make debugclean Remove source .o files and binary (preserves lib/sqlite3.o)
    make distclean  Remove build artifacts and generated Makefile
    make check      Run build check
    make dist       Create a release tarball
